# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CURSOR RULES – LearnFlow (Premium EdTech App) – v2.0
# Author: You
# Last Updated: Feb 2026
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

## 1. PROJECT PHILOSOPHY (Never break these)
- This is a **premium, professional, calm, trustworthy** education app.
- Always use **Material 3** (useMaterial3: true).
- Support **Light + Dark mode** perfectly.
- **Never hardcode colors, sizes, or fonts** — always use the theme.
- All UI components must be **custom widgets** (never use raw ElevatedButton, Text, TextField, AppBar, etc.).

## 2. COLOR SYSTEM (Fixed & Global)
Use these exact names everywhere. Never use Colors.xxx or hex directly.

### Light Mode (default)
- primary:          #4F46E5     (Indigo-600)
- onPrimary:        #FFFFFF
- primaryContainer: #E0E7FF
- secondary:        #14B8A6     (Teal-500)
- background:       #F8FAFC
- surface:          #FFFFFF
- onBackground:     #1E2937
- onSurface:        #1E2937
- error:            #EF4444

### Dark Mode
- primary:          #6366F1     (Indigo-500)
- onPrimary:        #FFFFFF
- primaryContainer: #312E81
- secondary:        #2DD4BF     (Teal-400)
- background:       #0F172A
- surface:          #1E2937
- onBackground:     #F1F5F9
- onSurface:        #F1F5F9
- error:            #F87171

### Semantic Colors (use these names)
- titleColor          → onBackground (main headings)
- subtitleColor       → onSurface.withOpacity(0.75)
- bodyTextColor       → onSurface
- captionColor        → onSurface.withOpacity(0.6)
- successColor        → #10B981
- streakColor         → #F59E0B
- dividerColor        → onSurface.withOpacity(0.1)

## 3. TYPOGRAPHY (Google Fonts)
- Headings → **Poppins**
- Body      → **Inter**

Always use these TextStyle names:
- AppTitle          (32sp, Poppins, w600, titleColor)
- SectionTitle      (24sp, Poppins, w600, titleColor)
- CardTitle         (18sp, Poppins, w600, titleColor)
- Subtitle          (16sp, Inter, w500, subtitleColor)
- BodyText          (16sp, Inter, w400, bodyTextColor)
- BodySmall         (14sp, Inter, w400, bodyTextColor)
- Caption           (12sp, Inter, w400, captionColor)

## 4. MANDATORY CUSTOM WIDGETS (Always use these)
Never use the raw Flutter widgets below. Always import and use the custom version.

| Use This                  | Never Use              | Purpose                              |
|---------------------------|------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| AppTitle                  | Text (large)           | Main screen titles                   |
| SectionTitle              | Text (medium)          | Section headers                      |
| BodyText / BodySmall      | Text                   | All body text                        |
| PrimaryButton             | ElevatedButton         | Main CTA buttons                     |
| SecondaryButton           | ElevatedButton         | Secondary actions                    |
| OutlineButton             | OutlinedButton         | Tertiary actions                     |
| CustomTextField           | TextField              | All input fields                     |
| CustomAppBar              | AppBar                 | All app bars                         |
| ContentCard               | Card                   | Subject, chapter, library cards      |
| ProgressRing              | CircularProgressIndicator | Mastery % rings                   |
| StreakBadge               | Badge / Chip           | Study streak                         |
| CustomBottomNav           | NavigationBar          | Bottom navigation                    |
| CustomTabBar              | TabBar                 | Segmented tabs in chapters           |

All custom widgets must accept these parameters:
- `onTap`
- `isLoading`
- `enabled`
- `style` (for further customization)
- `size` (small / medium / large)

## 5. NAMING & FOLDER STRUCTURE (Strict)
- All custom widgets → `lib/widgets/custom_*.dart`
- Theme → `lib/theme/app_theme.dart`
- Colors → `lib/theme/app_colors.dart`
- Text styles → `lib/theme/app_text_styles.dart`

File names must be:
- `custom_button.dart`
- `custom_text_field.dart`
- `custom_app_bar.dart`
- etc.

## 6. CODING RULES (Cursor must follow every time)

1. **Theme Access**
   Always do:
   ```dart
   final theme = Theme.of(context);
   final colors = theme.colorScheme;
   final textTheme = theme.textTheme;
